sailpoint.integration

Class ListResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.integration.RequestResult
      • sailpoint.integration.ListResult

  • public class ListResult
extends RequestResult
    Transfer object that is used to send back a list of results which may be sorted and paged. As such, this returns the total count of objects that would be returned in the list without paging.
